description: We need to find this little guy a new home.
Bentley is a 2 year old Poodle.
Sasuke is Itachi's brother, also 3 months old.
Killu the Great Pyranese needs a new owner.
Jupiter is looking for a new home.
Itachi is a 3 months old cat.
Chewy the Chihuaha is ready for a new family.
Java is a newly saved Pug.
